<div class="question">
<h2 class="question-title">瞎扯 · 鸡那么脏，那为啥鸡巢几乎没有蟑螂？</h2>

<div class="answer">

<div class="meta">
<img class="avatar" src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fc734cfcc0b308e24640f9b5a2d2316d_l.jpg?source=8673f162">
<span class="author">知乎日报</span>
