<div class="content">
<article class="Post-Main Post-NormalMain" tabindex="-1">
<div class="Post-RichTextContainer">
<div class="css-1od93p9">
<div class="css-376mun">
<div class="RichText ztext Post-RichText css-119fve5">Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1908102066179663619/answer/1909422097379341739" target="_blank">鸡那么脏，那为啥鸡巢几乎没有蟑螂？</a>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/ac99c0eff7835ac6d7cec7852dc5722e" target="_blank">@席萝</a> ：阁下可能对鸡的破坏力没什么概念</div>
</blockquote>
<figure>
<div><img class="content-image" src="https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-cd8dcbe035b79e195300d43d10f9a288_1440w.jpg" alt=""></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<figure>
<div><img class="content-image" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fbd993d9f03c9805115161db46df466b_1440w.jpg" alt=""></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
